'''Webster's Home Reference Library''' is a box set of three books&mdash;a [[dictionary]], a [[thesaurus]] and a spelling and grammar guide&mdash;from [[Geddes and Grosset]] (an imprint of The Gresham Publishing Company LTD.).  The dictionary contains 40,000 definitions, the thesaurus contains 150,000 synonyms, and the spelling and grammar guide contains 40,000 common mistakes.

